archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: Medium ICT motivation cView
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation: On this diagram you can see the motivation scenario, as it will be at mid-term, from the ICT point of view. The mid-term work packages are completed and they have produced their changing effects as new capabilities. The work packages that will produce the long-term changing are present. The long-term work packages will realize specific long-term capabilities, making the change into reality.
